OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FAn increase in type 2 diabetes across
OL,7,FEngland is being driven by obese young
OL,8,Fwomen, experts suggest.
OL,10,FGrowing numbers of young adults are
OL,11,Fdeveloping type 2 diabetes, a new
OL,12,Fstudy by Imperial College London
OL,13,Ffound, with the age group more likely
OL,14,Fto be overweight when diagnosed than
OL,15,Folder people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
