CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784729924
OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FAnalysing data from 2011 to 2024,
OL,7,Fresearchers discovered that although
OL,8,Fcases are falling in older adults -
OL,9,Fwho still make up the majority of new
OL,10,Fcases - cases are increasing rapidly
OL,11,Fin people under 40.
OL,13,FThe gender disparity was also evident,
OL,14,Fas cases increased by 69% in women
OL,15,Faged 20-29, compared to by 43% in men
OL,16,Fof the same age.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
