OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FThis shows a 3% yearly increase for
OL,7,Fwomen and 2.1% annual increase for men
OL,8,Fin that age group.
OL,10,FContrastingly, cases in people aged 60-
OL,11,F79 declined by 7% in men and 4% in
OL,12,Fwomen over the same 13-year period.
OL,14,FType 2 diabetes is a chronic metabolic
OL,15,Fdisease where the body has high blood
OL,16,Fsugar levels due to not producing
OL,17,Fenough of the hormone insulin, or the
OL,18,Finsulin does not function properly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
