CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784729924
OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FExcess body fat, age, ethnicity and
OL,7,Ffamily medical history are all
OL,8,Fcontributing factors.
OL,10,FThe disease can be put into remission
OL,11,Fwith a change in lifestyle, including
OL,12,Fexercise and weight loss.
OL,14,FThe findings, published in Lancet
OL,15,FRegional Health Europe, are the first
OL,16,Fto examine type 2 diabetes trends
OL,17,Facross the England population by
OL,18,Fbreaking it down by age, sex and
OL,19,Fethnicity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
