PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784729924
OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FResearchers said the rise was evident
OL,7,Facross all ethnicities, but mainly in
OL,8,Fwhite, Asian and black women aged 20
OL,9,Fto 29, and in white women aged 30 to
OL,10,F39.
OL,12,FThe body mass index (BMI) increase
OL,13,Fover time for adults with type 2
OL,14,Fdiabetes under 40 was more than double
OL,15,Fthat of those over 40.
OL,17,FThis implies generations of younger
OL,18,Fadults are developing type 2 diabetes
OL,19,Fat a more severe level of obesity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
