PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784729924
OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FDr Shivani Misra, lead author of the
OL,7,Fresearch by Imperial College London,
OL,8,Fsaid the earlier onset of severe
OL,9,Fobesity in young people is "increasing
OL,10,Ftheir type 2 diabetes risk in early
OL,11,Flife and pulling down their age at
OL,12,Fdiagnosis".
OL,14,FShe said GLP-1 weight loss drugs, such
OL,15,Fas Ozempic and Wegovy, are being
OL,16,Frecommended to help treat the
OL,17,Fmetabolic disease, but there is
OL,18,F"insufficient research" to prove how
OL,19,Feffective it is in preventing type 2
OL,20,Fdiabetes in adolescents and young
OL,21,Fadults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
