PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784729924
OL,3,CObese young women driving increase in
OL,4,Ctype 2 diabetes cases, study finds
OL,6,FHelen Kirrane, head of policy at
OL,7,FDiabetes UK, said the increase in
OL,8,Fyounger people is "deeply concerning".
OL,10,F"Any diagnosis of type 2 diabetes is
OL,11,Fserious, but it can be more aggressive
OL,12,Fin younger people, increasing the risk
OL,13,Fof devastating complications and
OL,14,Fcutting lives short," she warned.
OL,16,FKirrane said further action needed to
OL,17,Fbe taken by the government, "including
OL,18,Frestricting the promotion of unhealthy
OL,19,Ffood and creating environments that
OL,20,Fsupport healthier lives".
